    "section_testimonials_aHyNcK": {
      "type": "section-testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "text_kjdkAT": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>We had Fenceworks install an AconX trampoline, and the experience was solid. The team was efficient and professional throughout the process. They took the time to explain the different trampoline models and helped us choose the right one. Overall, great experience!</p>",
            "name": "Mike Harrington",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_B9Xyrk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Absolutely thrilled with Fenceworks and their trampoline service! From first inquiry to final installation, the process was seamless and professional. Jake expertly explained the different options and walked me through the possible add-ons. We ended up with the 14 ft double bounce with basketball hoop. The installation team was friendly, efficient, and made sure everything was safe and perfect. Our kids are absolutely thrilled, and we’re so happy with the final result. Highly recommend if you’re looking for a quality trampoline and top-notch service!<br/></p>",
            "name": "Jill Osborn",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_txx7DA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Working with Jake and the Fenceworks team has been a wonderful experience! Jake is so attentive and professional, coming multiple times to my home to ensure that our new trampoline was installed in the ideal and safest location of our yard. Our trampoline is incredible, top of the line quality and safety and I know will be enjoyed for many, many years. Our family has used Fenceworks for swingset installations as well as our experience has always been great. Their products, installation and customer service are superb and I would recommend Fenceworks to all of my family and friends!<br/></p>",
            "name": "Samantha Malach",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_DNm4yP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Excellent guidance and service. The delivery and installation process was seamless. My girls (11 & 8) love their new trampoline. I cannot give a higher recommendation than Jake and his team.</p>",
            "name": "Edison Reformado",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_PKDxeq": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>My alleyoop trampoline was installed about 8 years ago and has held up great! Fenceworks came out to replace a bent upright- installers always have been on time and do a great job - highly recommend!</p>",
            "name": "Linda B",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        }
      },
